Name: Get Over Blood
About the game: In this game your main aim is to climb up to the top of a tower. To do this, you should use a blood rope. Use your mouse to click on bleeding objects to throw the blood rope. Swing on the rope and get up to the places you want. The main features: - Climb the tower; - Use the blood rope to get to the top; - Different physical objects can help you or become obstacles.
